# Gmail address FROM which orders are sent (your sender account)
SMTP_USER=Alexander Smishko

# Gmail App Password (NOT your regular password!)
# How to get it:
#   1. Go to https://myaccount.google.com/security
#   2. Enable 2-Step Verification
#   3. Search "App passwords" → create one for "Mail"
#   4. Paste the 16-character code here (no spaces)
SMTP_PASS=MyBionerica2026

# Manager email — all orders arrive here
MANAGER_EMAIL=aleksandrsmisko63@gmail.com

# Port for the Express server (default 3001)
PORT=3001

VITE_OWNER_SIGNATURE=GreenRegion_Alex_2025_X7q

**⚠️ Важливо:**
- Файл має називатись `.env` (не `.env.example`)
- Додай `.env` у `.gitignore` — щоб не потрапив у GitHub:
```
# .gitignore
.env
